## Import


`aws_neptune_cluster_endpoint` can be imported by using the `cluster-identifier:endpoint-identfier`, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:neptune/clusterEndpoint:ClusterEndpoint example my-cluster:my-endpoint
```
